item.title: CBS Live Chat
item.description: [The following is saved quotes] Q - @ThatIsNotAnExit @CSI_CBS We’ve made a message page to jorja so were wondering if there’s a way she could get the link? It’s http://weloveyoujorjafox.tumblr.com/ #askjorja A - @CSI_CBS .@ThatIsNotAnExit We’re up and running in a few minutes. Send us your questions #AskJorja xx. Q - @JulesSweetzer working on the show for so long, do you feel like you could be a CSI in real life #AskJorja
